Text: 4. How many bulls do you see ?
To the park , to the park , the dog starts to bark . It can run ! It can run !

Text: Let's run and have some fun .

Text: There's a hole , there's a hole . It's that pig digging a hole ! It can dig ! It can dig ! It can dig a hole as deep .
中文翻譯: 有個洞，有個洞。那頭豬正在挖洞！它可以挖！它可以挖！它可以挖出這麼深的洞。

Text: To that hill , to that hill , The bull lies on the hill . It's asleep , it's asleep , it sleeps on the hill .
中文翻譯: 到 那座 山 去 , 到 那座 山 去 , 公牛 臥 在 山上 . 它睡著了，它睡著了，它在山上睡覺。

Text: Time to go , home we go .
See a goat walking silent and slow . Goat walks slow , goat walks slow , let's walk with our tippy toes .
中文翻譯: 看見一隻山羊靜靜地、緩慢地走著。山羊走得很慢，山羊走得很慢，我們踮起腳尖走路吧。

Text: One little , two little , three little donkeys ;
